
When building with clang-16:

    clang-16: error: unknown argument: '-fexperimental-new-pass-manager'

The flag was removed in
https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/commit/69b2b7282e92a1b576b7bd26f3b16
The new pass manager has been the default since clang 13.

